00:00:08.550 --> 00:00:13.229
So they say Merry Christmas is enjoyment for joy,

00:00:13.687 --> 00:00:18.970
out of peace comes the joy, light of joy, happiness,

00:00:19.090 --> 00:00:24.403
I wish peace for the whole world, the whole nation,

00:00:24.523 --> 00:00:31.536
to understand to give up all the strides, all the false battles,

00:00:31.656 --> 00:00:38.480
for money and for power, all wrong ideas

00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:41.820
that they are different from each other

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:46.908
and come under the banner of Sahaj Yoga

00:00:47.511 --> 00:00:51.797
and enter into the Kingdom of God,

00:00:52.984 --> 00:00:58.085
