00:00:58.230 --> 00:01:02.030
I wish peace to all of them, to all the countries,

00:01:02.150 --> 00:01:08.342
all the human beings, in their families, in their hearts,

00:01:08.686 --> 00:01:14.579
with their children, with all of them,

00:01:14.699 --> 00:01:17.204
let there be peace,

00:01:17.324 --> 00:01:21.756
let their heart emit peace,

00:01:22.162 --> 00:01:26.657
their tongues speak with peace,

00:01:26.777 --> 00:01:32.060
their eyes see nothing but peace.

00:01:36.045 --> 00:01:41.246
All this has to change, tremendous change has to take place,

00:01:41.366 --> 00:01:45.150
the whole universe has to take a different turn,

00:01:45.270 --> 00:01:50.716
all that is hatred, hateful, ugly, has to vanish,

00:01:50.836 --> 00:01:53.027
and the peace has to prevail,

00:01:53.147 --> 00:01:56.525
which is not the peace of the dead but peace of the living,

00:01:56.645 --> 00:01:59.829
that has to come of the wise.

00:02:01.429 --> 00:02:05.709
I bless all of you to be the channels of that peace,

00:02:05.829 --> 00:02:08.320
to be beautiful channels of that peace,

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:11.689
to be glorious channels of that peace,

00:02:12.255 --> 00:02:18.950
to be great children of your Mother, who is so proud of you.

00:02:19.182 --> 00:02:21.216
May God bless you.
